---
title: "Blog — VibeWarden"
description: "VibeWarden blog. Security guides, vibe coding best practices, and release announcements."
canonical: "https://vibewarden.dev/blog/"
navActiveId: blog
hasMobileNav: false
ogType: website
ogTitle: "Blog — VibeWarden"
ogDescription: "Security guides, vibe coding best practices, and release announcements."
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}


{% block pageStyles %}
<style>
    /* ===== Blog Index ===== */
    .blog-header {
      padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .blog-header h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .blog-header p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .post-list {
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .post-card {
      display: block;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .post-card:hover {
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
      border-color: var(--brand-purple);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .post-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .post-card .post-date {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .post-card .post-excerpt {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== Responsive ===== */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .blog-header { padding: 2rem 0 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="container">
      <div class="blog-header">
        <h1>Blog</h1>
        <p>Security guides, vibe coding best practices, and release announcements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="post-list">
        <a href="/blog/why-we-built-vibewarden/" class="post-card">
          <h2>Why We Built VibeWarden</h2>
          <div class="post-date">
            <time datetime="2026-03-31">March 31, 2026</time>
          </div>
          <p class="post-excerpt">
            Vibe coding changed how fast we build apps. It didn't change how hard it is to secure them. VibeWarden is a security sidecar that sits in front of your app and handles TLS, auth, rate limiting, WAF, and structured logging -- one binary, one config, zero code changes.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
